<div class="hero">
  <div class="eyebrow">Global Chromatic Identity State</div>
  <h1>GCIS</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">The open harmonic state standard for music applications</p>
  <p class="hero-desc">One file. One format. <strong>Root, mode, scale, and active notes</strong> — portable across any music tool, any platform, any AI. Created by Benjamin Ryan · Keys, Codes &amp; Modes™</p>
  <div class="cta">
